#

Classic Cheeseburger with Homemade Garlic Aioli and Sweet Potato Fries

$15.99
950 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

DairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

AmericanComfort FoodGrilling

Description

Juicy beef patty topped with melted cheese, crisp lettuce, and a creamy garlic aioli, served with crispy sweet potato fries.

Ingredients

  • Ground Beef (80% lean): 1 lb
  • Cheddar Cheese: 4 slices
  • Burger Buns (gluten-free): 4
  • Sweet Potatoes: 2 large
  • Olive Oil: 3 tbsp
  • Garlic: 4 cloves
  • Mayonnaise: 1/2 cup
  • Lettuce: 4 leaves
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Paprika: 1 tsp
